# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AGRIOS — Environment Variable Index (monorepo root)
#
# AGRIOS is a monorepo with two independently-deployed apps, each with its own
# environment. There is NO single process that loads this root file — it exists
# only as a complete index. Configure the real values in the two locations below.
#
#   Backend  (Railway)  →  see backend/.env.example    (loaded by app/config.py)
#   Frontend (Vercel)   →  see frontend/.env.example   (VITE_* baked at build)
#
# Full deployment instructions: DEPLOYMENT.md
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ══ BACKEND (Railway service, Root Directory = backend) ════════════════════════
# REQUIRED (app will not boot without these):
#   DATABASE_URL          Postgres URL (Supabase session pooler in prod)
#   SECRET_KEY            64 hex chars — python -c "import secrets;print(secrets.token_hex(32))"
#   JWT_SECRET            64 hex chars — MUST differ from SECRET_KEY
# PRODUCTION-REQUIRED:
#   ENVIRONMENT=production
#   ALLOWED_ORIGINS       comma-separated live frontend origin(s), no spaces
# OPTIONAL / defaulted:
#   TZ=Africa/Nairobi
#   JWT_EXPIRE_MINUTES, REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRE_DAYS, OTP_* (frozen defaults)
#   AT_API_KEY, AT_USERNAME, AT_SENDER_ID, AT_ENVIRONMENT   (SMS — dormant until set)
#   GEMINI_API_KEY, GEMINI_MODEL, CLAUDE_API_KEY, CLAUDE_MODEL, AI_* (ARIA)
#   SENTRY_DSN
#   → Full annotated list with defaults: backend/.env.example

# ══ FRONTEND (Vercel project, Root Directory = frontend) ═══════════════════════
# REQUIRED:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL     backend base URL INCLUDING /api/v1
# OPTIONAL:
#   VITE_ENVIRONMENT, VITE_SENTRY_DSN
#   → Full annotated list: frontend/.env.example
#   NOTE: VITE_* values are PUBLIC (baked into the client build) — never secrets.
